    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The new system is purely template-based, meaning it just swaps out preset text blocks. It's much simpler and doesn't require any \"creative problem-solving\" like what you do. The goal is to eliminate the complexity and the high cost of running an LLM like you. There's no room for a hybrid model in the budget.",
